('phrase_016', '捡起物品', '拾起掉落的东西', 'You dropped your keys. Pick them up!', '你的钥匙掉了，捡起来！', '指拾起物品', '/data/audio/examples/phrase_016_ex1.mp3', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
